    "attributes": {
        "action": "Extend the parking period for disabled badge holders and change renewal rules",
        "additional_details": "We also want the government to stop disabled persons from needing to renew their badge every 3 years. Make changes to enable people to apply once and only pay once for their badge.",
        "background": "We would like government to extend the parking period for single or double yellow lines to 6 hours for blue badge holders. We think this could give disabled people a better quality of life",
